  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.17.1\n\n### What happened?\n\nI'm trying to run the hardhat network in a standalone mode, but instead, I get a prompt to choose to create a javascript or typescript project. I'm following the instructions here: https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/docs/overview#running-stand-alone-in-order-to-support-wallets-and-other-software.\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\nRun `npx hardhat node` .\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/assets/16622558/573f51df-1e6a-4772-af15-67808e972356)\r\n\n\n### Search terms\n\n\"hardhat standalone network\", \"npx hardhat node\"",
